rizoma for Debian
-----------------

POS Rizoma Comercio use a PostgreSQL database to work. You will ned to know the password of the postgres users to setup the proper database using the programn rizoma-config. To set the password of the postgres user to this as root:

    # passwd postgres

And it will ask you for the new password which will be asked later on the rizoma-config.

